      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and project seekers! This vehicle is ready for its next chapter and offers a fantastic opportunity for someone looking to roll up their sleeves. While it currently needs significant mechanical and cosmetic care, it\u2019s a budget-friendly way to get started on a restoration journey or to find those hard-to-locate parts!",
