      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my reliable ride that's been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has plenty of life left in it! Whether you're commuting or heading out on a road trip, this beauty runs smoothly and looks great. It's been well-taken care of, so you can just hop in and go. I've loved driving this car, and I'm sure you will too. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a good home!",
      "price": 34500.0,
