    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver\u2019s specimen featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. The powertrain delivers linear torque through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable differential lock. Key enthusiast-grade preventative maintenance has been completed, including VANOS solenoid refreshing and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure torsional rigidity. The suspension geometry remains tight with updated bushings, offering the communicative feedback and neutral handling balance this chassis is celebrated for. While the aesthetics reflect its service as a spirited grand tourer, the mechanical vitals are robust and track-ready.",
      "price": 34500.0,
