    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2016 BMW M3 finished in Alpine White over a striking Sakhir Orange leather interior. This car has been a joy to own and is in solid, reliable condition throughout. The exterior paint retains a beautiful luster, though you will find a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel\u2014typical of a car that has been enjoyed on the open road. Inside, the cabin remains a premium environment; the leather is supple and the carbon fiber trim is free of cracks, with only light wear visible on the driver-side seat bolster. Every feature, from the head-up display to the heated seats, works exactly as it should. Mechanically, the car is excellent. It has a full service history, with a recent oil change and a fresh set of tires installed less than 2,000 miles ago. It starts perfectly, pulls hard through all gears, and has no pending maintenance needs. This is a turn-key performance sedan ready for its next owner to drive home today.",
